title: Exception Thrown When Exporting Data from Table with Highlight/Map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from an attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains highlights or maps.
EB: The software should export data from the table with highlights or maps without any exceptions or errors.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to a table that contains highlights or maps.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
